            <title>[SEC-3063] OnMissingBeanCondition avoid initializing beans</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-3063</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;OnMissingBeanCondition&lt;/tt&gt; should use BeanTypeRegistry.getNamesForType to avoid initializing any beans&lt;/p&gt;</description>
